Moblico's Mobile-Backend-as-a-Service platform was designed from the ground up with both the application developer and systems integrator in mind.
For the developer, using Moblico's REST APIs, you can quickly and cost effectively add application features to your new app and/or your existing applications. &nbsp;In addition the platform is built to make application integration with existing systems a snap. &nbsp;Moblico's Mobile-Backend-as-a-Service is hosted in a start-of-the-art data center with full redundancy and is scaled to manage the intensive work loads that are required to support mobile. &nbsp;
For systems integrators, the Moblico Mobile-Backend-as-a-Service easily integrates with any 3rd party or IT system via a pluggable framework and securely exposes back office IT data as a set of lightweight web services. Additionally Moblico can provide both SaaS and Licensed solutions.
